    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As magic flows through your body, it causes physical traits of your dragon ancestors to emerge. At 1st level, your hit point maximum increases by 1 and increases by 1 again whenever you gain a level in this class.</p>\n<p>Additionally, parts of your skin are covered by a thin sheen of dragon-like scales. When you aren't wearing armor, your AC equals 13 + your Dexterity modifier.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: This feature automatically increases your maximum hit points.</em></p>\n<p><em>You can change your Armor Class type to Draconic Resilience natively.</em></p>\n</section>",
